Vozaprime Index (Comprehensive)

Author: Gyouu Vozaprime
Status: Active, Evolving Framework
Date of Composition: Post-Ruvian Escape (Day 14)

Part I: Operational Rationale

This index is a comprehensive cognitive framework for the classification of all variables relevant to mission success. A fragmented analysis is a failed analysis. True efficiency requires a holistic system to instantly triage every element in this unit's operational theater.

This framework is divided into two primary branches:

Combat Triage (Indices VDCI, OOI, VCDI):

Function: Quantifies physical, magical, and temporal threats.

Query: "Can I fight this? What is the cost? What is the risk?"

Strategic Triage (Indices AUC, IVI):

Function: Quantifies non-combatant assets, resources, and information.

Query: "Is this useful to me? Is this data valuable?"

All analyses are cross-referenced to produce an instantaneous, multi-domain tactical decision.

